dataset.name: CBOT Soybean Oil, December 2015 (BOZ2015)
dataset.description:
Contract Size:60,000 pounds (lbs) (~ 27 metric tons)

Deliverable Good:Crude soybean oil meeting exchange-approved grades and standards-see exchange Rules and Regulations for exact specifications.

Tick Size:1/100 of a cent ($0.0001) per pound ($6.00 per contract)

Pricing Unit:Cents per pound

Columns: Open, High, Low, Settle, Volume, Previous Day Open Interest. Note that Open Interest is always reported for the previous trading day, to avoid lookahead bias.
